36#include "mech_locl.h"
37
38/**
39 * Compare two GSS-API OIDs with each other.
40 *
41 * GSS_C_NO_OID matches nothing, not even it-self.
42 *
43 * @param a first oid to compare
44 * @param b second oid to compare
45 *
46 * @return non-zero when both oid are the same OID, zero when they are
47 * not the same.
48 *
49 * @ingroup gssapi
50 */
51
52GSSAPI_LIB_FUNCTION int GSSAPI_LIB_CALL
53gss_oid_equal(gss_const_OID a, gss_const_OID b)
54{
55 if (a == b && a != GSS_C_NO_OID)
56 return 1;
57 if (a == GSS_C_NO_OID || b == GSS_C_NO_OID || a->length != b->length)
58 return 0;
59 return memcmp(a->elements, b->elements, a->length) == 0;
60}
